00:03:27.599 --> 00:03:28.520
Adelante.

00:03:31.360 --> 00:03:32.439
Si,

00:03:32.919 --> 00:03:34.199
Quiero decir,

00:03:35.080 --> 00:03:37.639
si me pasa algo y no estoy a tu lado,

00:03:38.400 --> 00:03:39.400
